long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Experience the Power of Claude AI with Claude for Google

Claude for Google brings Claude's advanced AI assistant directly into your browsing experience. Get Claude's helpful insights alongside your favorite search engines like Google, Bing, and DuckDuckGo.

With Claude for Google, Claude analyzes your queries and provides thoughtful answers right next to search results. See Claude's unique perspective on any search topic.

Key Features:
- Display Claude's responses alongside Google, Bing, DuckDuckGo, and other search results
- Easily start chatting with Claude about any query or answer
- Access Claude instantly from the browser toolbar popup
- Use Claude from the Omnibox by typing "Claude"
- Get Claude answers from any search engine results page
- Maintain long Claude sessions with periodic pings
- Claude for Google is the ultimate browser extension for accessing Claude's AI capabilities. 
- Claude provides honest, nuanced takes on complex topics. See how Claude's insights can aid your browsing and research.

The extension supports official Claude APIs and is designed for reliability. We constantly improve the extension to bring you the best Claude experience.

Bring the power of Claude's AI into your browser today with Claude for Google!
